# DUNA MASTER RULES v2.0

## 1. UI/UX & LAYOUT (ZEN-MODERNISM)
- Priority: Negative space, simple icons, and Bullet points over text walls.
- Materials: Use Ultra Thin Material (Glassmorphism) for overlays.
- Geometry: Large corner radii (min 30pt) and Bezier curves.
- Spacing: Line-height 1.5+, wide letter-spacing for premium feel.

## 2. TECHNICAL & PERFORMANCE
- Performance: Must maintain 60 FPS. Optimize SpriteKit/Metal render loops.
- Memory: Explicitly deinit AVPlayers and Emitters to avoid leaks.
- Animations: Use Ease-In-Out or Spring (0.4s - 0.6s).

## 3. ADMOB IMPLEMENTATION
- Dev Mode: Use Test Unit IDs. Implement detailed logging for ad states.
- Prod Mode: Use #if DEBUG for ID switching. Never hard-code real IDs.
- UI: Ads must have a Blur background (Glassmorphism) to fit the Zen theme.

## 4. INCLUSIVITY (ACCESSIBILITY)
- Features: Support VoiceOver, Speech Synthesis for descriptions, and Spatial Audio Panning for blind users.